{"tid":1566884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵無公開831拍到警察8分鐘畫面","createTime":"2019-09-13T20:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:31:08.000Z","uid":37554,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71bf885244bfd6fea9739ecabc28316a7b8accf5","tid":1566884,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:00:52.000Z","msg":"港鐵昨日公開 831 太子站的部分閉路電視截圖，其中影到警察出現在月台的一個鏡頭，有八分鐘時間沒提供任何畫面。警方及政府都否認有要求港鐵，不要提供這八分鐘的截圖，港鐵回覆指沒有補充。<br />\n<br />\n831 晚太子站究竟發生甚麼事？港鐵早前披露閉路電視截圖，希望釐清事實。其中一部閉路電視拍到，當晚十時五十六分警員抵達 4 號月台。同一個位置，下一張截圖已經是十一時零四分，即八分鐘後，見到仍然有警員站在月台，列車正駛走。兩張圖並排，這部閉路電視影到的是 4 號月台近車尾位置。<br />\n<br />\n回看當晚傳媒的片段，影到的主要集中在列車較前位置。那近車尾這一卡當時情況如何？警方有否執法？有沒有人受傷？由於有八分鐘的空白，我們看不到。為何不公開這八分鐘截圖？有沒有人要求港鐵不公開？警方及政府都指，沒要求港鐵不公開任何相關截圖，港鐵說沒有補充。<br />\n<br />\n至於警方當晚在 4 號月台近車頭及中間位置執法的過程，有線新聞台在太子站見到在這個位，有三支鏡頭有機會影到，但港鐵公開的二十多張截圖，沒有一張來自這三支鏡頭。究竟這三支鏡頭當時有否損毀，為何沒提供截圖，港鐵也不回應。<br />\n<br />\n除了警方落月台後的八分鐘，當晚十一時許救護員入站後到凌晨近一時，月台的情況是怎樣，閉路電視拍到甚麼，港鐵的截圖都沒有交代。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556935/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%84%A1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B831%E6%8B%8D%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F8%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556935%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B831%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F8%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%259D%25A2&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=44ef72d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556935%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B831%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F8%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%259D%25A2&h=e661f287\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556935/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%84%A1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B831%E6%8B%8D%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F8%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2</a>"},{"pid":"0e66c75bfc85eecc856cd436619d65660fa648e2","tid":1566884,"uid":12612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81a29aedda69e6089d8d04da546fcc7c3657ffee","tid":1566884,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caef243954402d4d211f4d3fa55c9ea3156f177","tid":1566884,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb56bb155062853cc5213fe0d3fb40e9b2584898","tid":1566884,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011a1649a31e680fd81c57e5adad08f38ada7b05","tid":1566884,"uid":117040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20b1a4bed346009165dba475ed33f34bd99e22b","tid":1566884,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}